			<h2>dos &amp; don'ts</h2>
			<p class="sub-heading">Not sure how to style it? A few simple can't-miss tips eliminate any "Am I doing this right?" fears.</p>

			<div class="details">
				<div class="image">
					<img src="/b/fashion/images/projects/denim/denim-styles/editorial-6.jpg" alt=""/>
					<a class="normal-brand-footer brand-footer" id="frame-wide-leg" href="/shop/product/?ID=2813073">FRAME</a>
					<a class="normal-brand-footer brand-footer second-brand" id="rag-and-bone-wide-leg" href="/shop/product/?ID=2813085">rag &amp; bone/JEAN</a>
				</div>
				<div class="copy">
					<h3>Wide-Leg Silhouettes</h3>
					<hr class="splitter"/>
					<p><strong>Do:</strong> Play with proportion. Try boosting the voluminous vibes with an equally ample tucked-in tee, or balance out the dramatic denim silhouette with a body-defining blouse that shows some skin.</p>
					<p><strong>Don't:</strong> Go too short with the crop--culottes these are not. By our calculations, the perfect wide-leg jeans should hit 1–3 inches above your ankle for maximum leg lengthening.</p>
					<a href="/shop/womens-apparel/jeans/Jean_fit_m/Wide%20Leg?id=5545" id="shop-wide-leg-jeans" id="shop-wide-leg-jeans" class="link">SHOP WIDE-LEG JEANS</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="details">
				<div class="copy">
					<h3>Bright Washes</h3>
					<hr class="splitter"/>
					<p><strong>Do:</strong> Showcase bright new pairs like the throwback heroes they are. We love the look the most when it embraces its ’90s-era casual-cool vibe paired with cropped hoodies and graphic tees (just skip the Discman).</p>
					<p><strong>Don't:</strong> Wear a large-scale printed blouse that looks more loud than luxe with such a bold jean. Chambray, color-blocked solids or neutral black and white tops keep the focus on your statement skinnies.</p>
					<a href="/shop/womens-apparel/jeans/Jean_trends/High-Impact%20Hues?id=5545" id="shop-hight-impact-hues-bright" id="shop-hight-impact-hues-bright" class="link">SHOP high-impact hues</a>
